reviewText: I was disapointed in the butcher bro.'s for 11 bucks they could have cut up a cow a pig and a chicken . The work they did is good but if you want to learn to butcher go to you tube and save your money . This DVD was a waste of money , in hard times like these you need more bang for your buck . Sorry BB you flubed a dub on this one - next time do the whole half of beef .
